data.description: This charming home boasts 3-4 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a spacious 2-car garage. Enjoy the privacy of a fenced backyard surrounded by majestic oak trees and a relaxing back deck.  This well cared for home is truly in ''move-in'' condition!  Conveniently located between Milwaukee & Chicago, 10 min.  to I-94 & 5 min. to the Antioch Metra Train Station to Chicago.  Come and take a look at this bright & cheerful home, you won't be disappointed!
